'''Hama University''' ({{lang-ar|'''<U+062C><U+0627><U+0645><U+0639><U+0629> <U+062D><U+0645><U+0627><U+0629>'''}}), founded in 2014  with 11 faculties, is a [[public university]] located in the city of [[Hama]], [[Syria]]. It was established by Presidential Decree No. 19 for 2014 issued by [[Bashar Al-Assad]].<ref>{{cite web|title=New university established in Hama, the sixth in Syria|url=http://sana.sy/eng/387/2014/05/13/544204.htm|publisher=http://sana.sy|accessdate=14 May 2014}}</ref>

